Discover the exceptional value and capabilities of this 2011 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited. With its powerful 5.7L HEMI V8 engine, 4-wheel drive, and impressive towing capacity, this SUV is ready to take on any adventure. Boasting an array of premium features, this Grand Cherokee is a true standout in its class.

Key features include:
Voice Recognition
Bluetooth Hands-Free
Local Trade
Trailer Tow Group IV
220 Amp Alternator
Heavy-Duty Engine Cooling
7 & 4 Pin Wiring Harness
Class IV Receiver Hitch
Rear Load Leveling Suspension

This well-equipped Grand Cherokee also offers a wealth of comfort and convenience features, such as the Media Center 430N navigation system, 10-speaker audio system, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a power driver's seat with memory. The premium leather-trimmed interior and heated front and rear seats add a touch of luxury, while the power moonroof and rear parking sensors enhance your driving experience.

Exterior highlights include the off-white paint, chrome exterior mirrors, and 18-inch polished aluminum wheels, giving the Grand Cherokee a refined and distinguished appearance. The Trailer Tow Group IV package further enhances its capabilities, with features like the 220-amp alternator, heavy-duty engine cooling, and a Class IV receiver hitch.

With its exceptional capabilities, premium features, and striking good looks, this 2011 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited is a remarkable value. Whether you're seeking a capable family SUV, a versatile weekend adventurer, or a premium luxury ride, this Grand Cherokee is sure to exceed your expectations. We invite you to experience its impressive performance and uncompromising quality firsthand. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover why this Grand Cherokee is the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

2011 Hyundai Elantra GLS Sedan in Red Allure Metallic

This 2011 Hyundai Elantra GLS is a great example of why the Elantra became one of the most popular compact sedans on the road. Finished in eye-catching Red Allure Metallic with a warm Beige interior, it offers a comfortable, efficient, and well-equipped driving experience that still holds up today.

Under the hood is a reliable 1.8L 4-cylinder engine paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission. This combination delivers smooth performance, excellent fuel efficiency, and low operating costs, making it an ideal choice for daily commuting, student drivers, or anyone looking for dependable transportation without unnecessary complexity.

Inside, the Elantra GLS surprises with thoughtful features and a spacious layout. The cabin includes cloth seating, an adjustable steering wheel, power windows and door locks, cruise control, and air conditioning. The rear seat pass-through adds flexibility for longer items, while interior storage solutions like door pockets, a center console with armrest, and a rear center armrest with cupholders make everyday use easy and comfortable.

This Elantra is equipped with the Navigation Package, which adds automatic headlights, a backup camera, an integrated navigation system, and a premium sound system, features that were well ahead of their time in this segment. The Preferred Equipment Package further enhances the experience with aluminum wheels, Bluetooth connectivity, steering wheel audio controls, and illuminated vanity mirrors.

Safety was clearly a priority, with features including front, side, and curtain airbags, anti-lock brakes with brake assist, traction and stability control, tire pressure monitoring, daytime running lights, and child safety locks. These systems work together to provide confidence and peace of mind for both driver and passengers.

On the exterior, this Elantra carries a clean, modern design with body-colored bumpers and door handles, heated power mirrors, tinted glass, and stylish aluminum wheels. It presents well and reflects Hyundais focus on blending efficiency with contemporary styling.

Optional equipment on this Elantra includes the Navigation Package, Preferred Equipment Package, floor mats, and iPod cable, all adding convenience and connectivity without complicating ownership.

If youre looking for a fuel-efficient sedan that offers comfort, strong safety features, and proven reliability, this 2011 Hyundai Elantra GLS is a smart and practical choice.

description: Discover the 2009 Chevrolet Impala 3.5L LT, a stylish and reliable sedan that combines comfort, performance, and modern features. With a sleek white exterior and a neutral beige interior, this used vehicle offers a spacious cabin with seating for five, making it ideal for families or daily commuters. Powered by a 3.5-liter V6 engine producing 211 horsepower, it delivers smooth acceleration and impressive fuel efficiency of up to 29 mpg on the highway. Equipped with a 4-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel drive, this Impala provides a confident driving experience whether navigating city streets or cruising on the open road. Its elegant design is complemented by body-color bodyside moldings and a sporty rear spoiler, adding to its aerodynamic appeal. Inside, the vehicle boasts a leather-wrapped steering wheel with audio controls and a flip-and-fold rear seat, enhancing convenience and comfort. The Luxury Edition Package further elevates the driving experience with leather-appointed front bucket seats and additional amenities, ensuring a refined ride. Satellite radio readiness adds a modern touch, providing endless entertainment options for every journey. This 2009 Chevrolet Impala is not only about style and comfort but also prioritizes safety and security. It features 4-wheel anti-lock brakes, which help maintain steering control during braking, especially in emergency situations. The vehicle also includes power door locks, offering added security and ease of use for all passengers. These safety features work together to provide peace of mind, making this sedan a dependable choice for daily driving and long trips alike. 2009 Chevrolet Impala Safety and Security Features The Impala is equipped with essential safety features, including 4-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS), which helps prevent wheel lockup during sudden stops and enhances overall stopping performance. Power door locks are standard, providing convenient security for all occupants and simplifying locking procedures. These features contribute to a safe driving environment, making this vehicle a reliable choice for those seeking peace of mind on the road. 2009 Chevrolet Impala Entertainment and Technology Features Entertainment and technology are well-covered in this Impala, featuring a premium sound system with a total of six speakers that deliver clear, immersive audio throughout the cabin. Satellite radio readiness ensures access to a wide range of stations and entertainment options, keeping passengers engaged on long drives. With these features, the Impala offers a comfortable and connected driving experience that complements its stylish design and smooth performance.
